author: liyin
msg: [master] Avoid "new" region server starvation during the region assignment
Currently, the RegionPlacement would use all the region server in the META table as the assignment domain. It may cause the starvation problem for the region server who just back from in-repair.
The fix is to add all the online region server into the assignment domain.
Test Plan: will test it on dark launch cluster
